models.name: Kids trumpet
models.description:
A small toy trumpet that sounds like a whistle. It isn't very loud.

The 2 part version requires a bit of assembly, but should have no issues with supports. Stick part 2 into the mouth of the trumpet to assemble.
The basic model may get supports stuck inside of it if they aren't used cautiously.

models.name: Speaker Adapter and Rainshield
models.description:
For Scion FR-S or Subaru BRZ front speakers, to fit Dayton RS180-4 speakers.  This design also adds a rainshield.  

It must be printed in 2 pieces, unless you have a large-format printer.  

Mounting holes were made intentionally small, so drill them out to fit the desired fasteners (I used standard M6 nuts and bolts)

models.name: Compass for drawing big circles
models.description:
Compass for drawing big circles, with a radius of max 600mm.

With one hole for a screw in the center of the circle, and holes every 10mm for a pencil.
